MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 37.09% to NT$5,090,075,000 from NT$8,091,071,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales           5,090,075        8,091,071   
YOY%             -37.09%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           45,261,368       49,250,446  
YOY%              -8.10% 
=================================================================
 